title: chapter4_intro
---
WASD: ?
WASD: This grove... I know this place, but... something in the roots has shifted.
WASD: This Dedicant who wears me... they are but a child.
WASD: A child, and yet... the anger in their heart eats at every nerve ending.
WASD: This one knows me by a different name... RDFG? Have I become something else to them?
RDFG: What am I now?
